WEBVTT

00:00:00.959 --> 00:00:02.236
There are things we say

00:00:02.261 --> 00:00:04.657
when we catch the eye of a stranger

00:00:04.681 --> 00:00:06.403
or a neighbor walking by.

00:00:07.530 --> 00:00:10.056
We say, "Hello, how are you?

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:11.788
It's a beautiful day.

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:13.001
How do you feel?"

00:00:13.552 --> 00:00:17.186
These sound kind of meaningless, right?
And, in some ways, they are.

00:00:17.210 --> 00:00:19.569
They have no semantic meaning.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.508
It doesn't matter how you are
or what the day is like.

00:00:23.934 --> 00:00:25.401
They have something else.

00:00:25.425 --> 00:00:27.312
They have social meaning.

00:00:28.051 --> 00:00:30.530
